{"tid":1474332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復紅土】連登仔又俾人用投票帶風向","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:58:37.000Z","uid":2010,"like":65,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd19483262259cc58b3003101a5cb4d6695caa2","tid":1474332,"uid":2010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"817光復紅土反對通知書已出，繼續定取消？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474042</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGJ3veA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGJ3veA.png&h=545c2ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此post樓主極為陰濕，<br />\n正評表面上贊成照去，但就<span style=\"color: gold;\">暗指你哋去咗都係跟劇本送頭</span>；<br />\n負評就係叫你哋「留力」，谷遊行<br />\n<br />\n紅磡、土瓜灣嘅唔係香港人？<br />\n佢哋飽受蝗害，光復行動一拖再拖，<br />\n我明白大家都想分析利弊後再去，<br />\n咁請你哋以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">討論</span></span>形式進行，而唔係單純<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正負評投票帶風向</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係人人都有時間追post追到尾，<br />\n佢哋一睇正負評就會以為真係取消咗，<br />\n咁樣開post投票話照去定取消係極不負責任，<br />\n請大家運用獨立思考，<br />\n唔好又倒退返去兩個月前連登投票決定散水嘅局面。<br />\n<br />\n以下請繼續<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">討論</span></strong>往後行動。"},{"pid":"fb74a23dfe227bcb06b39267f67d022db3d599c1","tid":1474332,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e118f08dad46b4246ded77663e85f34860b1c72","tid":1474332,"uid":16124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30a04ec19a1d836fff470d3bbe651cd8b307897e","tid":1474332,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b291d0776b0d6fc842a95af1fc741d2d6f6625a7","tid":1474332,"uid":83557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"817紅土繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji